install_msg:
This cog contains some random fun image generation commands. I hope you will enjoy them.

 **NOTE: This step is completely optional.**
 This cog has `eject` and `petpet` commands, which uses <https://some-random-api.ml> API and requires an API key.
 You can find out how to get one at: <https://some-random-api.ml/docs/Welcome/Keys>.

 Once you have received the API key, you can do:
```[p]set api srapi api_key <your_api_key>
```
name: ImageCog
short: Some random fun image generation commands.
